  "industry_note": "HDPE (High-Density Polyethylene, ρ 0.94-0.97). Tg ≈ -125°C, Tm 130-137°C, max service 80-100°C continuous. σy 22-30 / UTS 25-35 / El 200-800% / E 0.7-1.4 GPa. PE-100 grade (gas/water 배관 표준): σf 50-year creep ≥ 10 MPa. Water/gas piping (가장 흔한 plastic pipe — KS M3408 / ISO 4427), 화학 plant 탱크, milk/juice 병, 폐기물 통, 어망. Recyclable (PE-2 자원순환). Welding via butt-fusion 표준 (PE 의 가장 흔한 결합).",
